(278, 1, NULL, 'post', 'Tổng quan về vách xốp cách âm + Báo giá 2022', '{\"brief\":{\"vi\":\"L\\u00e0m th\\u1ebf n\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u00e1ch \\u00e2m 1 c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng? Hi\\u1ec7n nay c\\u00f3 r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u c\\u00e1ch \\u00e2m kh\\u00e1c nhau. M\\u1ed9t trong s\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u00f3 b\\u1ea1n kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ecf qua l\\u00e0 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e1ch x\\u1ed1p c\\u00e1ch \\u00e2m. Khi \\u00e2m thanh \\u0111i qua c\\u00e1c v\\u00e1ch x\\u1ed1p, ch\\u00fang s\\u1ebd l\\u00e0m ti\\u00eau t\\u00e1n n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u00e2m thanh. Do \\u0111\\u00f3, n\\u00f3 s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap cho kh\\u00f4ng gian c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean y\\u00ean t\\u0129nh h\\u01a1n.\"},\"content\":{\"vi\":\"<p>Hai smartphone \\u0111\\u1eaft nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a Samsung s\\u1ebd c\\u00f3 gi\\u00e1 r\\u1ebb h\\u01a1n 400 USD so v\\u1edbi th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<article>\\r\\n<p>Theo b\\u00e1o c\\u00e1o c\\u1ee7a&nbsp;<em>SamMobile<\\/em>&nbsp;nh\\u1eb1m ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn smartphone m\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh g\\u1eadp c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 ho\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh m\\u1ee5c ti\\u00eau 7 tri\\u1ec7u m\\u00e1y c\\u1ee7a hai model khi ra m\\u1eaft,&nbsp;Galaxy Z Fold 3&nbsp;v\\u00e0&nbsp;Galaxy Z Flip 3&nbsp;s\\u1ebd r\\u1ebb h\\u01a1n 20% so&nbsp;Z Fold 2&nbsp;v\\u00e0&nbsp;Z Flip. Theo \\u0111\\u00f3, Galaxy Z Fold 3 s\\u1ebd c\\u00f3 gi\\u00e1 1.599 USD v\\u00e0 Z Flip 3 l\\u00e0 959 USD.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<figure data-size=\\\"true\\\" itemprop=\\\"associatedMedia image\\\" itemscope=\\\"\\\" itemtype=\\\"http:\\/\\/schema.org\\/ImageObject\\\"><img alt=\\\"Samsung \\u0111ang d\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u1ea7u th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u1ec1 smartphone m\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh g\\u1eadp. \\u1ea2nh:Phonearena.\\\" data-ll-status=\\\"loaded\\\" data-src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-sohoa.vnecdn.net\\/2021\\/06\\/08\\/insider-hints-at-likely-samsun-1694-1549-1623088597.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=bYAMpJ-8yHbcRV_gkntPng\\\" intrinsicsize=\\\"680x0\\\" itemprop=\\\"contentUrl\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i1-sohoa.vnecdn.net\\/2021\\/06\\/08\\/insider-hints-at-likely-samsun-1694-1549-1623088597.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=bYAMpJ-8yHbcRV_gkntPng\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<figcaption itemprop=\\\"description\\\">\\r\\n<p>Samsung \\u0111ang d\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u1ea7u th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u1ec1 smartphone m\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh g\\u1eadp. \\u1ea2nh:&nbsp;<em>Phonearena.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/figcaption>\\r\\n<\\/figure>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Hai model n\\u00e0y s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang b\\u1ecb chip x\\u1eed l\\u00fd m\\u1edbi nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a&nbsp;Qualcomm&nbsp;- Snapdragon 888. Z Flip 3 ch\\u01b0a c\\u00f3 th\\u00f4ng tin v\\u1ec1 c\\u1ea5u h\\u00ecnh, c\\u00f2n Z Fold 3 s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang b\\u1ecb 12 GB RAM v\\u00e0 b\\u1ed9 nh\\u1edb trong 256 GB.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Z Fold 3 c\\u00f3 m\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh ngo\\u00e0i 6,21 inch, m\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh trong nh\\u1ecf h\\u01a1n so v\\u1edbi th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc, c\\u00f2n 7,55 inch. M\\u00e1y s\\u1ebd c\\u00f3 pin 4.380 mAh, h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 s\\u1ea1c nhanh 25W. M\\u00e1y ch\\u1ea1y&nbsp;Android 11&nbsp;khi ra m\\u1eaft v\\u00e0 s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c n\\u00e2ng c\\u1ea5p l\\u00ean&nbsp;Android&nbsp;th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 m\\u1edbi trong 3 n\\u0103m.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Z Flip3 s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang b\\u1ecb m\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh ch\\u00ednh 6,9 inch, t\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 l\\u00e0m t\\u01b0\\u01a1i 120 Hz v\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 vi\\u1ec1n m\\u1ecfng c\\u00f9ng camera tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc d\\u1ea1ng \\u0111\\u1ee5c l\\u1ed7 nh\\u1ecf h\\u01a1n. M\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh b\\u00ean ngo\\u00e0i c\\u0169ng t\\u0103ng k\\u00edch th\\u01b0\\u1edbc. \\u0110i k\\u00e8m l\\u00e0 pin 3.900 mAh.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>N\\u1ebfu n\\u0103m nay&nbsp;Samsung&nbsp;khai t\\u1eed d\\u00f2ng Galaxy Note, Z Fold 3 s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 S Pen v\\u00e0 b\\u00fat n\\u00e0y s\\u1ebd t\\u00edch h\\u1ee3p trong m\\u00e1y. H\\u00e3ng c\\u0169ng s\\u1ebd s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng k\\u00ednh si\\u00eau m\\u1ecfng UTG th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ee9 hai v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u1ec1n cao h\\u01a1n cho Z Fold 3.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Galaxy Z Flip 3 s\\u1ebd s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u1ee5m camera gi\\u1ed1ng&nbsp;Galaxy S21, v\\u1edbi camera ch\\u00ednh v\\u00e0 camera g\\u00f3c si\\u00eau r\\u1ed9ng 12 megapixel, camera tele 64 megapixel v\\u1edbi kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng zoom hybrid 3x. Galaxy Z Fold 3 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 trang b\\u1ecb camera gi\\u1ed1ng&nbsp;S21 Ultra. Ngo\\u00e0i ra, model n\\u00e0y c\\u0169ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang b\\u1ecb camera \\u1ea9n d\\u01b0\\u1edbi m\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Theo&nbsp;<em>Ice Universe<\\/em>, s\\u1ef1 ki\\u1ec7n Unpacked c\\u1ee7a Samsung c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 di\\u1ec5n ra v\\u00e0o gi\\u1eefa ho\\u1eb7c cu\\u1ed1i th\\u00e1ng 6. Hai model Galaxy Z Fold 3 v\\u00e0 Z Flip 3 s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c giao \\u0111\\u1ebfn kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng trong th\\u00e1ng 7.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/article>\"},\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_keyword\":null,\"seo_description\":null}', 'https://noithattugia.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/cach-am-phong-karaoke.jpg1_-601x400.jpg', NULL, 1, 16, NULL, 'active', 1, 1, '2023-02-03 01:39:10', '2024-01-07 18:26:56', 'tong-quan-ve-vach-xop-cach-am-bao-gia-2022');
