(388, 1, NULL, 'post', 'Các mẫu biệt thự nhà vườn cấp 4 đẹp mà bạn không thể bỏ qua', '{\"brief\":{\"vi\":\"Nh\\u1eefng n\\u0103m g\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u00e2y, bi\\u1ec7t th\\u1ef1 nh\\u00e0 v\\u01b0\\u1eddn c\\u1ea5p 4 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nhi\\u1ec1u gia ch\\u1ee7 Vi\\u1ec7t l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn. B\\u1edfi thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf nh\\u00e0 n\\u00e0y mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn kh\\u00f4ng gian s\\u1ed1ng tho\\u1ea3i m\\u00e1i, phong c\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u1eb9p v\\u00e0 m\\u1edbi m\\u1ebb.\"},\"content\":{\"vi\":\"<h2><b>Kh\\u00e1i ni\\u1ec7m bi\\u1ec7t th\\u1ef1 nh\\u00e0 v\\u01b0\\u1eddn c\\u1ea5p 4<\\/b><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Bi\\u1ec7t th\\u1ef1 nh\\u00e0 v\\u01b0\\u1eddn c\\u1ea5p 4 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf sang tr\\u1ecdng, ti\\u1ec7n nghi v\\u1edbi ki\\u1ebfn tr\\u00fac h\\u00e0i h\\u00f2a v\\u1edbi khung c\\u1ea3nh thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean. Th\\u00f4ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/noithattugia.com\\/biet-thu-nha-vuon\\/\\\"><strong>bi\\u1ec7t th\\u1ef1 nh\\u00e0 v\\u01b0\\u1eddn<\\/strong><\\/a>&nbsp;th\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng tr\\u00ean di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch l\\u1edbn, thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf th\\u00f4ng minh, phong th\\u1ee7y h\\u00e0i h\\u00f2a c\\u00f9ng n\\u1ed9i th\\u1ea5t ti\\u1ec7n nghi tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn l\\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng cho nhi\\u1ec1u gia \\u0111\\u00ecnh hi\\u1ec7n nay.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><img alt=\\\"bi\\u1ec7t th\\u1ef1 nh\\u00e0 v\\u01b0\\u1eddn\\\" aria-describedby=\\\"caption-attachment-48598\\\" height=\\\"634\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/noithattugia.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/11\\/biet-thu-nha-vuon-cap-4-2.jpg\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/noithattugia.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/11\\/biet-thu-nha-vuon-cap-4-2.jpg 900w, https:\\/\\/noithattugia.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/11\\/biet-thu-nha-vuon-cap-4-2-568x400.jpg 568w, https:\\/\\/noithattugia.com\\/wp-content\\/